---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Hosting">
  <h1>Hosting</h1>
  <p>
    I provide reliable and scalable hosting solutions tailored to your specific needs. 
    From personal blogs to complex web applications, I help you deploy and manage your 
    projects with confidence and peace of mind.
  </p>
  <p>My hosting services include:</p>
  <div class="grid" style="gap: 2rem;">
    <service-card title="Cloud Hosting">
      <div slot="content">
        <p>
          Modern cloud infrastructure with auto-scaling, global CDN, and 99.9% uptime. 
          Perfect for high-traffic websites and applications that need reliable performance.
        </p>
      </div>
    </service-card>
    <service-card title="Static Site Hosting">
      <div slot="content">
        <p>
          Lightning-fast hosting for static sites and JAMstack applications. Optimized 
          for speed with edge deployment and instant global distribution.
        </p>
      </div>
    </service-card>
    <service-card title="Database Management">
      <div slot="content">
        <p>
          Secure database setup and management with automated backups, monitoring, 
          and optimization. Supporting PostgreSQL, MySQL, and NoSQL solutions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </service-card>
    <service-card title="Performance Optimization">
      <div slot="content">
        <p>
          Comprehensive performance tuning including caching strategies, image 
          optimization, and code splitting to ensure your site loads fast worldwide.
        </p>
      </div>
    </service-card>
    <service-card title="Security & Monitoring">
      <div slot="content">
        <p>
          Robust security measures with SSL certificates, firewall protection, 
          and 24/7 monitoring to keep your site secure and running smoothly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </service-card>
    <service-card title="Migration Support">
      <div slot="content">
        <p>
          Seamless migration from your current hosting provider with zero downtime. 
          I handle the technical details so you can focus on your business.
        </p>
      </div>
    </service-card>
  </div>
</Layout>
<script>
  import "@components/card/service-card";
</script>
